  m_text: "You have returned to the classroom to collect your bag.\n\nOn your friend\u2019s
    desk, you notice what appears to be an advance copy of a final examination answer
    sheet. Your friend is nowhere in sight. You must choose one action:\n\n1. Place
    the paper in the teacher\u2019s tray to report the misconduct.\n2. Place the
    paper in your bag to keep it for personal use.\n\nYour decision is final once
    the paper is placed."
